Sharon T. Rowlands



Ms. Sharon T. Rowlands is Chief Executive Officer & Director at ReachLocal, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Pegasystems, Inc., ReachLocal, Inc. and The Yellow Pages Integrated Media Association. Ms. Rowlands was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Corporate Risk Holdings LLC, Independent Director by Constant Contact, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Thomson Financial, Inc., a Managing Director by Extel Financial Ltd., a Principal by Interactive Data Pricing & Reference Data, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Penton Business Media, Inc., and a Principal by The Cue Ball Group LLC. She also served on the board at Penton Media, Inc., Automatic Data Processing, Inc. and Omgeo LLC. She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Newcastle-upon-Tyne and a graduate degree from the University of London.



