Executive Profile
Sharon T. Rowlands  Chief Executive Officer of ReachLocal, Gannett Co., Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 5 Board Members in 5 different organizations across 14 different industries.See Board Relationships58$1,899,597As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Ms. Sharon T. Rowlands has been the Chief Executive Officer of ReachLocal, Inc. at Gannett Co., Inc. since April 1, 2014. Ms. Rowlands serves as an Advisor of The Cue Ball Group, LLC. Ms. Rowlands has more than 20 years of experience leading multi-billion dollar companies serving small and medium-sized businesses, financial markets and enterprise customers. She served as the Chief Executive Officer of Penton Business Media Holdings, Inc. Ms. Rowlands served as the Chief ... Executive Officer of Kroll Ontrack, Inc. since September 2011. She served as Chief Executive Officer of Corporate Risk Holdings, LLC (alternate name, Altegrity, Inc.) at USIS, LLC from September 2011 to 2014. She served as the Chief Executive Officer of Penton Media, Inc., from October 7, 2008 to 2011. Ms. Rowlands served as the Chief Executive Officer of Thomson Financial, Inc. from April 2005 to April 2008 and served as its President from 2000 to April 2008 and Chief Operating Officer. Prior to Thomson Financial, Ms. Rowlands served as Managing Director of Thomson Financial Database Group in Europe. She joined Thomson Financial in 1996. She ran the North American operation of FT Information and served as Managing Director of Extel Financial. She served in the financial information industry for more than 22 years. Prior to her career in the financial industry, she served for three years as a high school teacher and one year in trade publishing. She serves as a Director of Penton Business Media Holdings, Inc. She serves as Director of American Business Media, Inc. Ms. Rowlands  has been a Director of Pegasystems, Inc., since April 13, 2016 and Junior Achievement of New York, Inc. since 2006. Ms. Rowlands served as a Director of ReachLocal, Inc. from April 1, 2014 to August 9, 2016. Ms. Rowlands served as a Director of Corporate Risk Holdings, LLC since November 2011. She served as a Director of Constant Contact, Inc. from July 2010 to May 20, 2014. She also served as Director of Penton Media, Inc. since October 7, 2008. She served as a Member of Advisory Board at Ultimate Escapes, Inc. She served as a Director of Automatic Data Processing, Inc. from April 30, 2008 to September 23, 2011. She served as a Member of Advisory Board at Ultimate Resort, LLC. She served as a Member of Global Board of Managers at Omgeo LLC until June 2008. In 2005, she received the Women's Bond Club Merit Award. Ms. Rowlands holds Bachelor of Arts Honors degree in History from Newcastle University and a Post Graduate Certificate of Education from the University of London's Goldsmiths College.Read Full Background




